  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the shredded tandoor chicken and cook until heated through.",
    "Add the cooked quinoa, caraway seeds, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and stir in the remaining 1 tablespoon of butter until melted.",
    "Transfer the quinoa mixture to a serving dish and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
